Ɓe ze, ɓay ká Ŋgɛrɛwṵru ɓaa pola lew ɓáy faa nzoɓ ya̰aŋa ɓay saa nzi-ɛ na, ɗo munu ɓáy zaɗɛ. Ka ɓaa mii: «Mì mgbúɗa nzaa-i ɓay ɓáa ɓay ɓáy faa law ɓay. Feri ká ɗo zaɗ muni ɓa piɛɗke lew hɔy ɓáy ɗáa tusiri na, Mì tína sa̰w ɓayke kaɗ kaɗ ɓa kɛlɛ
