Ɔ́rɔ ɓie nam ká tusiri key kara a ɗoko munu nda̰w. Leɗ nzaapeɗri ká nulue na i ví wál sakra nzoɓ law mgbɔ́rɔri ɓáy nzoɓri ká i ɗaa fe ɓáy zaɗɛ ká nun Ŋgɛrɛwṵru na ɗo ɓoɗ ɓoɗ.
