Báyḭi lɛ, Zezu kɔ-kɔ́m rie falɛ gbuk ɓáy law fa̰a. Law-ɛ kara sɛ ni mgbuk mgbuk ɓay tul law-ri ká ŋgɔŋ na. Ze a ɓaa ha̰ leɗban na mii: «Ndáɗa nduo-ɔ!» Lɛɛ, leɗban na ndaɗa nduo-ɛ na, lɛ, nduo-ɛ na vaa ɓáy kere.
Zaɗka Fariziri kɔ Zezu ká vaa leɗban na ku báyḭi lɛ, i tḭi saa ɓil hul mbṵ́ kḭ í vǎa ziŋ Ziɓ ha̰nɛri ká i zuɔ fal Mbay *Eroɗ, a í nzaa faa ɓay ika Zezu.Ruɔ nzoɓri vi pol Zezu
