Ɗo faa mbḭw munu nda̰w, ɓari nzoɓri ká i rìi sakra ɓaarì hiyaw hiyaw na, feri ká vi tul-ri ɓa lɔm na kuɔ ri ha ri ɗáake fe ɗáa kɔn naysuo nda̰w, í ḭ̌m hṵrusuo Ŋgɛrɛwṵru nda̰w, a í tḭ̌irike nzoɓ riŋ ɗikari ká nulue nda̰w pi.
