Ì kɔ, ɓa ɓari nzoɓkeri ku na ze, i ɗaa ha̰ téke ɓil kḭ ɗo. Kɔn fe ɗáa naysuo ze re mbay ká tul-ri ɓo, i ɗo ɓáy Tem Ŋgɛrɛwṵru ya.
