Falɛ lɛ, leɗ nzaapeɗ Ŋgɛrɛwṵru ndeke ɗi niŋke se a vǎa kuna him hɛrɛ Ŋgɛrɛwṵru ká ɗo ɓil tuŋguo ɓe na zuɔ tul síe a ha̰ ni faa zɔ́kɔ nzoɓri pǐi ɓáy zaŋa ɓe.
