Falɛ lɛ, leɗ nzaapeɗ Ŋgɛrɛwṵru ndeke ɗi ndeɓeke se a vǎa kuna him hɛrɛ Ŋgɛrɛwṵru ká ɗo ɓil tuŋguo ɓe na zuɔ tul kariŋgaw mbay fe mgbam na, ha̰ puoruo ɓe ɗo ɓil suŋ nduŋ. Nzoɓri sṵ rḭm-ri mgbɔkli mgbɔkli ɓay kɔ́kɔ sɛkɛ fe ɓari,
