Piriri ɓáy nzoɓ káw tul-riri ká mì kɔ ri ká ɓil fe ká tina nun ha̰ mì na, i ɗo mini key: i ɗo ɓáy gari lari ká ŋgɔŋ kɔkyɔ ɓa sḭ́ɛ nda̰w, ɗo ŋgul nda̰w, a ɓa tawori nda̰w pi. Tul piriri na, ɗo munu ɓa tul mbakiri. Huu ɓáy zuu huu, rɔɔ ɓáy tisaw ká vuo huu a fṵ kpiri kpiri tḭi saa ɓil law nzaa-ri wulam wulam.
Ɓáy faa fe nuri ká say ká tḭi saa ɓil law nzaa piriri, ká ɓa ɓíɛ ká mbi ɓáy zaɗri na, nzoɓri ká i te ɓil-e zaɗ say na, zaɗ mbḭwke zǐŋke huɗ,
ɓay ḭi lɛ, hṵrusuo piriri na ɗo ɓil law nzaa-ri ɓáy sa̰w-ri. Sa̰w-ri na rìi sɔyri ká i ɗo ɓáy tul ɓay ɗáake sɛkɛ ziŋ nzoɓri.
A ɓie nzoɓri ká i hu-huɗ ɓíɛkeri ká mbi ɓáy zaɗ ku ya na, i suo kér ɓay ɓari ká tul peɗ ka̰aya ɓari ya. I ruo temndayari, ɓáy feri ká i kɔ ɓa wṵru ɓari ká i ɗaa ɓáy kḭri lariri ɓoɗ ɓoɗ ká ndṵy nda̰w, tisaw nda̰w, rɔɔ puu nda̰w na, ɓa pola pola. Ɓa feri ká i kɔ-kɔ́m ya nda̰w, í láa ɓay ya nda̰w, a í se-seɗ ya nda̰w pi.
Nzoɓkeri ku na, i suo kér ɓay ɓari ká tul ika nzoɓ ya nda̰w, fe ɗáa mgbḭi ɓari ya nda̰w, fe ɗáa lɔrɔ ɓari ya nda̰w, mase riiɓa ɓari ya nda̰w pi.
